=head1 DESCRIPTION

Preferences for migrating a database to AWS.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Heterogeneous => L<Paws::MigrationHubStrategy::Heterogeneous>

Indicates whether you are interested in moving from one type of
database to another. For example, from SQL Server to Amazon Aurora
MySQL-Compatible Edition.


=head2 Homogeneous => L<Paws::MigrationHubStrategy::Homogeneous>

Indicates whether you are interested in moving to the same type of
database into AWS. For example, from SQL Server in your environment to
SQL Server on AWS.


=head2 NoPreference => L<Paws::MigrationHubStrategy::NoDatabaseMigrationPreference>

Indicated that you do not prefer heterogeneous or homogeneous.



